  "2318660": {
    "name": "Which Way Up: Galaxy Games",
    "steam_appid": 2318660,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2318660/extras/0dfafe8646cb4e4b58f851e3675aeb37.avif?t=1749534908\" width=616 height=222 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Which Way Up: Galaxy Games》是一款适合家庭的派对游戏，通过让你在墙壁和天花板上奔跑、围绕行星轨道旋转、或者穿越重力场飞越整个关卡，为玩家提供了独特的行动自由。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >我们的 12 个“重力游戏”中，每一个都提供了独特的迷你挑战，最多可容纳 4 名玩家同台竞技。在你穿越重力场时，将朋友们弹射到太空中，用整个月球进球得分，在行星间跳跃以逃离黑洞，捕获并守住星座图案，还有更多精彩玩法！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2318660/extras/80d3b2f113e0120033ecf0f09e838834.avif?t=1749534908\" width=680 height=76 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 支持最多 4 名玩家的重力平台玩法，可以本地游玩或通过 Steam Remote Play Together 在线游玩</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 7 名被称为“天体精灵”的角色（在试玩版中解锁 5 名）</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 适合各个年龄段的家庭和朋友，欢乐无穷</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 12 个银河游戏（试玩版中解锁 6 个），包括：</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2318660/extras/f93e56637caf3a94467e8469e8cdd87c.avif?t=1749534908\" width=616 height=127 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2318660/extras/086e48ee763621774b99c098ce06f6b4.avif?t=1749534908\" width=616 height=312 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2318660/extras/dc08b73463d2f76c57d6c8f9bac3a4bf.poster.avif?t=1749534908\" width=616 height=166 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2318660/extras/dc08b73463d2f76c57d6c8f9bac3a4bf.webm?t=1749534908\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2318660/extras/dc08b73463d2f76c57d6c8f9bac3a4bf.mp4?t=1749534908\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2318660/extras/0f279323a827bb36e8bf9941e457c7af.avif?t=1749534908\" width=616 height=536 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2318660/extras/cfec6f948d3d287df1acbbd7df0a3b6b.poster.avif?t=1749534908\" width=616 height=166 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2318660/extras/cfec6f948d3d287df1acbbd7df0a3b6b.webm?t=1749534908\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2318660/extras/cfec6f948d3d287df1acbbd7df0a3b6b.mp4?t=1749534908\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2318660/extras/0382ccd76085ff184d08280d3f02947c.avif?t=1749534908\" width=616 height=566 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2318660/extras/0222c35efe29501ee5fa47e27d085930.poster.avif?t=1749534908\" width=616 height=166 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2318660/extras/0222c35efe29501ee5fa47e27d085930.webm?t=1749534908\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2318660/extras/0222c35efe29501ee5fa47e27d085930.mp4?t=1749534908\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2318660/extras/1d1ae67426b7dc1b1b526418c7dc4129.avif?t=1749534908\" width=616 height=560 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2318660/extras/9f1b12ed7baf140f1b371bb8ae2d0fd4.poster.avif?t=1749534908\" width=616 height=166 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2318660/extras/9f1b12ed7baf140f1b371bb8ae2d0fd4.webm?t=1749534908\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2318660/extras/9f1b12ed7baf140f1b371bb8ae2d0fd4.mp4?t=1749534908\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2318660/extras/36bbc46050239e47ff644382492f2760.avif?t=1749534908\" width=616 height=566 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2318660/extras/3a944ba1d3377ef2420258e6415e93ab.avif?t=1749534908\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2318660/extras_big/3a944ba1d3377ef2420258e6415e93ab.avif?t=1749534908 width=800 height=214 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2318660/extras/f198984bf02d7ae7ed8b3e679b8ff6f0.avif?t=1749534908\" width=616 height=566 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2318660/extras/1ab4a3fb1177d874fe53588b4e280d42.avif?t=1749534908\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2318660/extras_big/1ab4a3fb1177d874fe53588b4e280d42.avif?t=1749534908 width=800 height=214 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2318660/extras/30304344696dbfb48a9362532cc4a11a.avif?t=1749534908\" width=616 height=290 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2318660/extras/92e769ac3991b9e5e2eca740d2b6f4cb.poster.avif?t=1749534908\" width=616 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2318660/extras/92e769ac3991b9e5e2eca740d2b6f4cb.webm?t=1749534908\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2318660/extras/92e769ac3991b9e5e2eca740d2b6f4cb.mp4?t=1749534908\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2318660/extras/8254e7a44f312117d771be5466a81441.avif?t=1749534908\" width=680 height=76 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2318660/extras/a76e6947bf27619a38cd921aa93f9494.poster.avif?t=1749534908\" width=616 height=116 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2318660/extras/a76e6947bf27619a38cd921aa93f9494.webm?t=1749534908\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>在宇宙诞生之前，天体精灵们一个接一个聚集在一起，实现一个梦想：生命的梦想。然而，宇宙是不可预测的，而创造生命是一项艰辛的工作。因此，天体精灵们为自己创造了一种消遣方式：“银河游戏”。这些年轻的天体精灵们互相竞赛和训练，以学习如何有朝一日成为它们各自宇宙概念的化身。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><table><tr><td><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2318660/extras/fa8ee299fceb7911efeeb4d830e7fd6f.avif?t=1749534908\" width=150 height=128 /></span></p></td> <td><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>萌芽</strong></h2>萌芽是生命科学和有机生命的化身，是大自然和所有生物的拟人化表现。</p></td> </tr> <tr><td><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2318660/extras/c2a5d1131187f9249d1e985936148c0a.avif?t=1749534908\" width=150 height=128 /></span></p></td> <td><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>棱镜</strong></h2>棱镜是光的化身，是人类肉眼可以感知的电磁辐射的拟人化表现。</p></td> </tr> <tr><td><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2318660/extras/9ef2fcc004cf3e75d5a5b023e12fbedd.avif?t=1749534908\" width=150 height=128 /></span></p></td> <td><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>露娜</strong></h2>露娜是地球唯一的天然卫星的化身，是夜晚和地球潮汐变化的象征。</p></td> </tr> <tr><td><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2318660/extras/be351d63c023a90a690a15582fef141b.avif?t=1749534908\" width=150 height=128 /></span></p></td> <td><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>阳阳</strong></h2>阳阳是太阳系中心那颗恒星的化身，为我们的星球提供光和能量。阳阳和棱镜关系亲密，他们共同为萌芽带来了生命。</p></td> </tr> <tr><td><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2318660/extras/4c43abba511000f18825f1aaa03881a0.avif?t=1749534908\" width=150 height=128 /></span></p></td> <td><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>小磁</strong></h2>小磁是磁场的化身，能够使物体相互吸引或排斥。小磁拥有将人们聚集在一起或保持距离的力量。</p></td> </tr> <tr><td><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2318660/extras/b7936d71e6ad0b9357b8e4e2a9c3bc5a.avif?t=1749534908\" width=150 height=128 /></span></p></td> <td><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>星火</strong></h2>星火闪耀了数百万年，并在每个星系中吸引了狂热的追随者。星火被认为是所有天体精灵中最闪亮的存在。</p></td> </tr> <tr><td><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2318660/extras/debd19024c1caee65572ff47b9210516.avif?t=1749534908\" width=150 height=128 /></span></p></td> <td><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>轨道</strong></h2>轨道是物体在受到重力影响时在太空中所遵循的弯曲轨迹的化身。轨道有时会短暂停留，有时却永不离开。</p></td> </tr></table><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2318660/extras/4738ea54822bdb362609ba2d74cd891e.poster.avif?t=1749534908\" width=616 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2318660/extras/4738ea54822bdb362609ba2d74cd891e.webm?t=1749534908\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2318660/extras/4738ea54822bdb362609ba2d74cd891e.mp4?t=1749534908\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
